Package: context-synthesizer
Version: 0.1.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv, python3-pip, adduser
Maintainer: Out-of-Bound Chronicles <dev@localhost>
Description: Context Synthesizer — Claude API proxy with prompt-cache telemetry
 Local gateway for Claude CLI (Mode B). Pins Claude.md, manages history
 compaction, and logs bifurcated token/cost metrics for every successful
 /v1/messages request to /var/lib/context-synthesizer/stats/telemetry.jsonl.
 .
 Configure Claude CLI: ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8080
